    "content": "We've added \"View All\" buttons for the **Locations**, **Devices**, and **Referrer** sections on the Link Stats page.\n\nWhen clicked, this opens up a modal that lets you explore all data points for a given section via a fuzzy search interface. Here's an [example](https://dub.co/stats/github).\n\nThis is helpful for sections like `City` that tend to have a lot of data points. Instead of scrolling through a long list, you can now search for a specific city.\n\nLearn more about [how you can create links](/help/article/how-to-create-link) and [beautiful stats pages](/help/article/public-stats-pages) like this on Dub.",
